design:
Key decisions: (1) 3-node topology (CPU dev box node-a + NVIDIA GPU host node-b + CPU worker node-c) wired statically into each other's [[peer]] blocks per ARCHITECTURE.md v1. Default daemon port 7421 (confirmed by implementer against plan 01). (2) Five scenarios as shell scripts under examples/multinode/scenarios/ that source lib/assert.sh, check prereqs, run the command, capture stdout/stderr/exit, assert, print OK. (3) Compose-based smoke runs in CI: examples/multinode/ci/{compose.yaml,Dockerfile.node,nvml-stub.c,smoke.sh}. NVML stub is an LD_PRELOAD shim exposing nvmlInit_v2, nvmlDeviceGetCount_v2, nvmlDeviceGetHandleByIndex_v2, nvmlDeviceGetName, nvmlDeviceGetMemoryInfo_v2, nvmlDeviceGetUUID, nvmlShutdown — reports a single fake 24 GiB device. (4) Manual sign-off via human checklist for hardware-dependent scenarios 4 and 5 (real PCI BDF set, real GPU PACK timing). (5) New xtask subcommand: `cargo xtask demo-smoke` chains release build -> nvml-stub.so build -> docker compose up -> compose exec driver smoke.sh -> compose down -v -> exit. Scenarios 4 and 5 NOT run in smoke (require real device files). (6) Demo programs are intentionally tiny: cuda_hello.cu (single CUDA kernel printing 'hello from gpu <ord> on node <hostname>', host-only stub when CLASSIC_NVML_STUB=1) and pci_lspci_loop.c (pure libc, opens namespace path, lists PCI BDFs 10x with 100ms sleep). (7) Coordinator helper for scenario 3 lives inline as a generated bash one-liner installed by `make setup` — no new shipped binary.

Topology: subnet 10.42.0.0/24, node-a 10.42.0.10 (dev box, no GPU), node-b 10.42.0.11 (1x NVIDIA >= 16 GiB VRAM), node-c 10.42.0.12 (CPU worker). All three peers static-wired. Daemon port 7421.

CLI surface (consumed, not added): classic spawn --requires, --pack, --bind-remote, --service, --node; classic ps; classic mail; classic kill. Spellings inherit from plans 04/07.

File layout:
examples/multinode/{README.md, Makefile, lib/assert.sh}
examples/multinode/config/{node-a,node-b,node-c}.toml
examples/multinode/programs/{cuda_hello/{Makefile,cuda_hello.cu}, pci_lspci_loop/{Makefile,pci_lspci_loop.c}}
examples/multinode/scenarios/{01-hw-affinity,02-no-match,03-service-lookup,04-namespace-bind,05-pack-group}.sh
examples/multinode/ci/{compose.yaml, Dockerfile.node, nvml-stub.c, smoke.sh}
xtask/src/{main.rs (MODIFIED — registers demo-smoke), demo_smoke.rs (NEW), nvml_stub.rs (NEW)}
